                  </Tab>
                  <Tab text="Math Hard">
                    <content>
                      <AnchorPane minHeight="0.0" minWidth="0.0" prefHeight="180.0" prefWidth="200.0">
                           <children>
                              <TextArea editable="false" prefHeight="378.0" prefWidth="467.0" text="                                               LEVEL 4: ALGEBRA&#10;&#10;WARNING!!!! THIS LEVEL IS INTENDED FOR PEOPLE WITH A SMALL &#10;BACKGROUND IN MATHEMATICS TO CHALLENGE THEIR MATHEMATICAL SKILLS&#10;WHILE PRACTICING TE REO MAORI. IF YOU HAVE MATHEMATICAL ANXIETY OR &#10;ANY RELATED CONDITION, DO NOT PROCEED BEYOND LEVEL 3.&#10;&#10;This level introduces algebra. In each question, an equation with a single variable&#10;will be displayed. Each equation may have one or more solutions, however in each&#10;and every case, only ONE solution will be an integer between 1 and 99 inclusive. &#10;As with previous levels, you can skip, record, re-record and replay yourself saying&#10;the positive integer solution in Te Reo Maori, by pressing the relevant buttons. &#10;You can check your answer, and as before, you are given a chance to retry if you &#10;get it wrong the first time.&#10;&#10;The total number of questions in this level is 15. If you get more than 12, you can &#10;proceed to the next level. In either case, you can replay this level.&#10;&#10;Good luck!" AnchorPane.bottomAnchor="5.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="5.0" AnchorPane.rightAnchor="5.0" AnchorPane.topAnchor="5.0" />
                           </children>
                        </AnchorPane>
                    </content>
                  </Tab>
